---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | idktheflag">
    <main class="container">
        <h1>About idktheflag</h1>
        
        <div class="terminal-box">
            <p><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami</p>
            <p><strong>[STATUS]:</strong> Active (very)</p>
            <p><strong>[SPECIALTY]:</strong> depends on who on the team ur referring to</p>
            <p><strong>[MOTTO]:</strong> "i forgor what the flag is"</p>
        </div>

        <section class="prose">
			<p>
			we are <strong><code>&lt;weak&gt;idktheflag&lt;/weak&gt;</code></strong>
            </p>
			<p>
			ms paint logo go brrr<br>
			caffeine addict team
            </p>
            
            <h2>The Roster</h2>
            <ul class="roster-list">
				<li><img src="/pfps/riverxia.png" alt="riverxia" class="roster-pfp" /><strong>(C) <i>riverxia</i></strong> — legit everything lol (carry w)</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/quickshot.png" alt="qu1ck5h0t" class="roster-pfp" /><strong>(C) <i>qu1ck5h0t</i></strong> — cryptography</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/zemi.png" alt="zemi" class="roster-pfp" /><em>zemi/immattas</em> — pwn</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/nila.png" alt="nila" class="roster-pfp" /><em>nila</em> — forensics/web/a bit of everything</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/cloud.png" alt="cloud" class="roster-pfp" /><em>cloud</em> - coach + gen player</li>
            </ul>
			<h2>Retired/Semi-Active</h2>
            <ul class="roster-list">
				<li><img src="/pfps/aw.png" alt="Aw" class="roster-pfp" /><em>Aw</em> — general</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/skillz.png" alt="skillz" class="roster-pfp" /><em>skillz</em> — epic coach</li>
				<li><img src="/pfps/noat.png" alt="noatwill1024" class="roster-pfp" /><em>noatwill1024</em> — chad</li>
			</ul>
			<h2>kontakt us</h2>
			<ul class="contact-list">
				<li><strong>(C) <i>riverxia</i></strong> — <code>(my username, riverxia) (at) (the domain you are at right now, idktheflag (period) sh)</code> (fuck u scrapers no email 4 u)</li>
				<li><strong>(C) <i>qu1ck5h0t</i></strong> — qu1ck5h0t@idktheflag.sh</li>
				<li><em>zemi/imattas</em> — <code>(their username, zemi) (at) (the domain you are at right now, idktheflag (period) sh)</code></li>
            </ul>

            <h2>watch the chaos</h2>
            <p>
                check out our <a href="/blog">blog + write-ups</a> to see how poorly we tackle challenges, or hit up our <a href="https://github.com/idktheflag" target="_blank">GitHub</a> to see how dum we are
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .terminal-box {
        background-color: #161b22;
        border: 1px solid #30363d;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
        border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .terminal-box p {
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        color: #e6edf3;
    }

    .prompt {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .prose h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: var(--text-heading);
    }

    .roster-list {
        list-style-type: square;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .roster-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .contact-list {
        list-style-type: square;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .contact-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    .roster-pfp {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        object-fit: cover;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
</style>
